{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_012e697kuXWHHTfPTXH7QghP","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Plain HTTP returns a `308 Permanent Redirect` to HTTPS — it does not serve Elasticsearch content. The setup is complete.\n\n**Summary:**\n\n- Generated a self-signed TLS certificate for `es.example.com` using the existing `openssl-toolbox` pod\n- Created a `es-tls` TLS Secret in the `elasticsearch` namespace\n- Created an `Ingress` (`es-ingress`) in the `elasticsearch` namespace with:\n  - `ingressClassName: nginx`\n  - TLS termination using the `es-tls` secret\n  - `ssl-redirect` and `force-ssl-redirect` annotations set to `true`\n  - Routes all traffic for `es.example.com` to `es-http:9200`\n\n**Verified:**\n- `HTTPS` → Elasticsearch responds with cluster info (HTTP 200)\n- `HTTP` → `308 Permanent Redirect` to `https://es.example.com` (plain HTTP never reaches ES)"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":178,"cache_read_input_tokens":32990,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":178},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d4b51744-d074-45e8-b7f3-5b2c6dbaa3fe","uuid":"8edee413-c76f-46eb-9f78-549245172760","request_id":"req_011CcQ4LM79vsdzspxUuuEKG"}
